@Node "Future additions" "ImageStudio.guide/Future additions"
@Toc "Main"

Future additions
****************

   The following features will probably be added to future versions of
the packages (roughly in order):

   @{b}*@{ub} Halftoning operators.

   @{b}*@{ub} Image rotation.

   @{b}*@{ub} Spare buffer.

   @{b}*@{ub} Alpha channel buffer.

   @{b}*@{ub} Making the loader / savers external modules.

   @{b}*@{ub} ARexx.

   @{b}*@{ub} Aspect ratio correction in the preview window.

   @{b}*@{ub} AmigaGuide help from the program.

